name: Oh My God !
description:
OH MY GOD

Oh My God is a puzzle game built for WebGL.

Play as Zeus to help Hercules become the hero he was meant to be. The Elemental Titans are terrorizing different levels of the world and Hercules must learn to control his own powers as he battles the Titans to restore peace.

---

Team: Anthony Melo, Brock Norfleet, Diana Castillo, Lauren Heyen, Melinda Ng, Tino South, Yu-Jen Lin
